{
  "stem": "3380.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, out, out, that they-- that they had the machine guns ready.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they chased us out, and we start marching again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from that point on, the next day they turned over to the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS was afraid to come in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was too close from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I find out later on that the next morning-- we left about 3 o'clock in the morning-- maybe three hours later the Russians came in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in process of marching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we still were marching on to the SS, and the shooting was going on just-- just as like it was before.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Whoever couldn't work was killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we marched [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from Blechhammer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how many days this took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got into a camp, Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went into lots of cities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I went to a city that was Goldberg town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Germany, Goldberg-- I mean, that-- it's, you know, very unusual.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not in-- they-- they tried to hide from the cities.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tried to go around places to eliminate the cities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember we went to certain cities what I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Goldberg I do remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Beautiful German cities.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember also [NON-ENGLISH] we used to go through, a city, and march.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we got into Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As we came in, transport was shipped out from Gross Rosen away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They gave us a half of bread and a piece of meat, and we were transported.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some people they put in-- we all went in cattle cars, naturally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some were open without a roof.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some were closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When we got in-- took us about five or six days-- we got into Weimar.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
